      <item>
        <title>Campaigning: Using &#39;Fediverse Rising&#39; banner text elsewhere</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[aschrijver]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Yes, I made them on a whim on January 1. You can use them freely. Didn’t license them or anything, CC0 then <img src="https://socialhub.activitypub.rocks/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9" title=":slight_smile:" class="emoji" alt=":slight_smile:"></p>
<p>Here’s the square version I used in a couple of toots:</p>
<p><img src="https://socialhub.activitypub.rocks/uploads/default/original/1X/fe29fa6f19ee06b873203d5e189ddda84005eeac.png" alt="fediverse-rising-2021-year-of-the-fedizen" data-base62-sha1="AgrdmmRlxFMZ7Itr4SehOLTxpnK" width="464" height="410"></p>
<p>Note: We can turn this into a veritable year-long campaign, make it bigger. I recommend the hashtag <span class="hashtag">#YearOfTheFediverse</span> which I am using myself.</p>
<p>PS. I also have Inkscape SVG’s, but they don’t attach to this post.</p>
<p><strong>Edit</strong>: <a class="mention" href="/u/how">@how</a> modified forum settings. Here are the SVG’s:</p>
<p><img src="https://socialhub.activitypub.rocks/uploads/default/original/1X/cda7f5a4a05a1f74117e74b265755463931db921.svg" alt="fediverse-rising-2021" data-base62-sha1="tljJs3aNnyU238wNKbqs2bwSOsx" width="690" height="101"></p>
<p><img src="https://socialhub.activitypub.rocks/uploads/default/original/1X/fd7842cf3318857986fb6d31deefb906d9666f32.svg" alt="fediverse-rising-2021-square" data-base62-sha1="AaisorDg8uuHwPi8pSC1OEbJLG2" width="405" height="358"></p>
<hr>
<p>PS. <a class="mention" href="/u/zleap">@zleap</a> you might mention the <a href="https://git.feneas.org/feneas/fediverse/-/wikis/watchlist-for-activitypub-apps">ActivityPub Watchlist</a> which is the input to Fediverse Party (I co-maintain it). It is more complete than for instance the awesome pages. Nice article!</p>
